@startuml
!include ../include/diagram-style.puml

title Search Trails

actor "End User" as EU
boundary SearchPanel
control TrailService
database Database

EU -> SearchPanel : enter criteria (optional)
EU -> SearchPanel : Search or Refresh

SearchPanel -> TrailService : searchTrail(criteria)
note right
  Empty criteria returns all trails
  (same as viewTrails when blank).
end note

TrailService -> Database : findTrails(criteria)
Database --> TrailService : matchingTrails
TrailService --> SearchPanel : matchingTrails

SearchPanel --> EU : list display

@enduml
